# FRC KAIZEN — About Us Section Design Prompt

> **Scope:** This document covers only the **About Us** section rebuild — a split editorial layout inspired by the ADM Design & Build reference. It replaces the earlier asymmetric stat-column layout with a more polished, tab-driven, two-column design.

