### Animated Headline

Three separate lines, each sliding up with staggered delay on scroll entry.

**Content:**
- Line 1: `"Built for"`
- Line 2: `"the Grid."`
- Line 3: `"Engineered to Win."`

**Typography:** `font-display`, `text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl`, `font-bold`, `text-white`, `leading-[1.05]`

**Framer Motion:**

```tsx
const lineVariants = {
  hidden: { y: 40, opacity: 0 },
  visible: (i: number) => ({
    y: 0,
    opacity: 1,
    transition: {
      delay: i * 0.2,
      duration: 0.7,
      ease: [0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94],
    },
  }),
}

// Usage
{['Built for', 'the Grid.', 'Engineered to Win.'].map((line, i) => (
  <motion.h2
    key={line}
    custom={i}
    variants={lineVariants}
    initial="hidden"
    whileInView="visible"
    viewport={{ once: true }}
    className="block font-display font-bold text-white ..."
  >
    {line}
  </motion.h2>
))}
```

