### Tab Navigation

Four tabs with animated active indicator and `AnimatePresence` content transitions.

**Tab labels:** `Who We Are` · `Our Car` · `Our Team` · `Our Story`

**Typography:** `font-body text-sm uppercase tracking-wider`

**Active state:** white text + red `2px` bottom underline  
**Inactive state:** `text-[#6b7280]`, hover → white

```tsx
const tabs = ['Who We Are', 'Our Car', 'Our Team', 'Our Story']

<div className="mt-10 border-b border-white/10">
  <div className="flex gap-8">
    {tabs.map(tab => (
      <button
        key={tab}
        onClick={() => setActiveTab(tab)}
        className={`
          relative pb-3 font-body text-sm uppercase tracking-wider
          transition-colors duration-200
          ${activeTab === tab ? 'text-white' : 'text-[#6b7280] hover:text-white'}
        `}
      >
        {tab}
        {activeTab === tab && (
          <motion.div
            layoutId="tab-underline"
            className="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-[2px] bg-red-600"
          />
        )}
      </button>
    ))}
  </div>
</div>
```

