### Value Card Stack

Four stacked full-width cards with staggered entry animation.

**Card data:**

| # | Title | Subtitle |
|---|---|---|
| 01 | Engineering Precision | Every system designed with intent |
| 02 | Performance First | Data-driven decisions, always |
| 03 | Iteration & Growth | Kaizen — constant refinement |
| 04 | Racing Spirit | Built for the grid, ready to compete |

**Container (Framer Motion stagger):**

```tsx
const containerVariants = {
  hidden: {},
  visible: { transition: { staggerChildren: 0.12 } },
}

<motion.div
  variants={containerVariants}
  initial="hidden"
  whileInView="visible"
  viewport={{ once: true }}
  className="flex flex-col gap-0"
>
  {cards.map(card => <ValueCard key={card.id} {...card} />)}
</motion.div>
```

**Individual Card:**

```tsx
const cardVariants = {
  hidden:  { x: 60, opacity: 0 },
  visible: { x: 0, opacity: 1, transition: { duration: 0.5, ease: 'easeOut' } },
}

function ValueCard({ id, title, subtitle }) {
  const [hovered, setHovered] = useState(false)

  return (
    <motion.div
      variants={cardVariants}
      onMouseEnter={() => setHovered(true)}
      onMouseLeave={() => setHovered(false)}
      className={`
        group flex items-center justify-between
        px-6 h-[88px]
        bg-[#111111]
        border border-[#1f1f1f] border-l-2
        transition-all duration-300 ease-out
        cursor-default
        ${hovered
          ? 'border-red-600 translate-x-1'
          : 'border-l-red-600'
        }
      `}
    >
      {/* Left: number + divider + text */}
      <div className="flex items-center gap-5">
        {/* Number badge */}
        <span className={`
          font-display text-3xl leading-none
          transition-all duration-300
          ${hovered ? 'text-red-600 opacity-100' : 'text-red-600 opacity-30'}
        `}>
          {id}
        </span>

        {/* Vertical separator */}
        <div className="w-px h-8 bg-white/10" />

        {/* Title + subtitle */}
        <div>
          <p className="font-display text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-white leading-tight">
            {title}
          </p>
          <p className="font-body text-xs text-[#6b7280] mt-0.5">
            {subtitle}
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Right: arrow icon (appears on hover) */}
      <motion.span
        animate={{ opacity: hovered ? 1 : 0, x: hovered ? 0 : -6 }}
        transition={{ duration: 0.2 }}
        className="text-red-600"
      >
        <ChevronRight size={16} />
      </motion.span>
    </motion.div>
  )
}
```

