## Design Checklist

Before committing the section, verify:

- [ ] All text elements use exactly one of: `font-brand`, `font-display`, `font-body`
- [ ] No `border-radius` other than `rounded-none` on any card or image
- [ ] Cards enter from `x: 60` (right side), not from below
- [ ] Divider dot pulses on loop — not a static circle
- [ ] Tab underline uses `layoutId="tab-underline"` for smooth slide
- [ ] `useInView` with `once: true` on all scroll animations
- [ ] Section background is `#0a0a0a`, not `black` or `bg-black`
- [ ] Card number opacity is `30%` at rest → `100%` on hover
- [ ] ChevronRight icon animates in on hover (`opacity 0 → 1`, `x: -6 → 0`)
- [ ] Body copy uses `font-body`, not `font-display`
- [ ] Red is used only for: eyebrows, number highlights, active tab, card left border, divider dot

